  <name>KneadNet</name>
  <summary>Convert electronic schematics into breadboard layouts and routing suggestions</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="zh-CN">将电子原理图转换为面包板布局和布线建议</summary>
  <description>
    <p>KneadNet reads KiCad project data and suggests component placements and jumper-wire routes for solderless breadboards.</p>
    <p>Its assembly view links schematic nets, breadboard positions, components, and routing steps to help users build the resulting circuit.</p>
    <p xml:lang="zh-CN">KneadNet 读取 KiCad 工程数据，为免焊面包板生成元件摆位和跳线布线建议。</p>
    <p xml:lang="zh-CN">装配视图会关联原理图网络、面包板孔位、元件和布线步骤，帮助用户搭建生成的电路。</p>
  </description>
